{"tid":48512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【俄使遇刺】緊張片段曝光！槍手伸手入袋拔槍 原來曾三度猶豫又放棄","createTime":"2016-12-21T06:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T07:09:04.000Z","uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb5c6d2c81069c782b99899bb268e24be4cdaac","tid":48512,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"土耳其22歲休班警員阿爾滕塔什（Mevlut Mert Altintas）槍殺俄羅斯駐土耳其大使卡爾洛夫（Andrei Karlov）前的片段曝光，見到他站在卡爾洛夫身後、面對與會眾人，多次伸手入西裝內袋似是想拔槍，但曾三度猶豫，最後終於把卡爾洛夫殺死。<br />\n<br />\n穿上西裝的阿爾滕塔什一開始站在卡爾洛夫的左後方，他雙手整理西裝東張西望，後來伸手入西裝似是想準備拔槍，但很快縮手。阿爾滕塔什之後緊握雙手佇立一會，開始走到卡爾洛夫的右後方，再次拉開西裝伸手入去並低頭查看，之後又放下雙手。<br />\n阿爾滕塔什當着眾多賓客的面前，冷靜地走到在卡爾洛夫身後，沒人懷疑過他正密謀暗殺。<br />\n大約10秒後阿爾滕塔什又再伸手入西裝，之後舉手摸摸鼻子，裝作若無其事。猶豫了三次之後，大約半分鐘後阿爾滕塔什終於迅速拔槍並擺好射擊姿態，瞄準卡爾洛夫連開多槍，此時畫面一片混亂，現場傳出多下槍聲及尖叫聲。<br />\n阿爾滕塔什過去兩年半在安卡拉警隊負責防暴工作，因出示警察證件而順利通過保安檢查進入展覽場地。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161221/56073124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161221%2F56073124&d=q3wpS3Rju0vDUCG9chlp3XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=61e76245\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161221%2F56073124&h=9f22c5d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161221/56073124</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3866e5c1b3bbcdfb21928517a33a25898a61e6f","tid":48512,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"扮保鑣咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82e752c10e8a9feb74a03e55d4ae895057dfabd","tid":48512,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮保鑣咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友一早已經扎哂馬手fing fing咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1849571dfca22f4733299e5c379302fa4664eab9","tid":48512,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扮保鑣咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友一早已經扎哂馬手fing fing咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過竟然係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要休班"},{"pid":"714803f81d65c18660fb887dcc68e5bc4f3fd3eb","tid":48512,"uid":20224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"休班警員"},{"pid":"261b2d7987748218e5a4fd61fbb62c404b63e209","tid":48512,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"諗深一層<br />\n休班警帶配槍真係bug黎"},{"pid":"b0920a6b8b0750abd8a0ed9b772982083d4b3e36","tid":48512,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港班鍵國撚應該學下野"},{"pid":"227ca6f1f68fc51b813692ce89f50ca7fbdc5a00","tid":48512,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗深一層<br />\n休班警帶配槍真係bug黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪臭係"},{"pid":"8be5a0d29e5239c1567aea39df25e4e754b4f042","tid":48512,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a2e2484d79654dbc1975b24846046fb49d90e